{"tid":1940791,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭：「封關」一詞在不同人士不同時段有不同闡述 是人流措施令香港數月來安然渡過","createTime":"2020-03-24T04:11:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T05:33:41.000Z","uid":21470,"like":3,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"9ac6d99965c0c52278328849b52c7667a0675898","tid":1940791,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T04:11:18.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥：政府逐步擴大封關才令香港早前相對安然渡過疫情<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥在開行政會議前強調，政府實施關口管制措施，都是按疫情發展和科學數據，按專家意見制訂。被問到政府加強封關措施是否後知後覺，<span style=\"color: gold;\">她表示，過去不同人對封關有不同說法，每段時間都有不同意思</span>，當疫情在內地爆發時，政府已控制內地和香港的跨境人流，令香港2月至3月初可以相對安然渡過，但目前又有輸入個案，防疫焦點就放在機場，因此明日凌晨起將禁止非本地居民入境。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1275990&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1275990%26csid%3D261_341&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1qix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=df374c2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1275990&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"98fb67adce467d1f24c150a9ed9f125aa2379c65","tid":1940791,"uid":218215,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T04:14:52.000Z","msg":"張建宗：「疫情受控」= 嚴密監控疫情<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c439015610ea5fc286fb1e316f213ceaf60d6e29","tid":1940791,"uid":201027,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T04:14:56.000Z","msg":"屌你老母啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbcd224a9966d48b6dc13cef3de757ef3e148a63","tid":1940791,"uid":2772,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T04:15:06.000Z","msg":"好在有屯門色魔 唔係一早世界末日"},{"pid":"2d15c6ffa4e231bc33699899daa9b2cbb3428ab1","tid":1940791,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyT